★ KEY LAYOUT RULES:
───────────────────
✓ Keep ADC inputs away from high-current paths
✓ Use short, direct traces from sensors to ADC
✓ Ground plane under all ICs
✓ Bypass caps close to power pins
✓ Twisted pair for OneWire if cable > 1m
✓ I2C pull-ups close to ESP32
✓ Separate analog and digital grounds (if possible)
